title: Muthoot Finance Q3 results: Net profit up 4% at Rs 1,044 cr - Economic Times
content: Muthoot Finance Q3 results: Net profit up 4% at Rs 1,044 cr  Economic Times
description: Muthoot Finance on Saturday reported a rise of 4 per cent in its consolidated net profit at Rs 1,043.60 crore in the quarter ended December 2021. The Company's net profit stood at Rs 1,006.60 crore in the corresponding quarter a year ago.
